OL,5,G1100 It Should Happen to You
OL,6,     F(1954) Judy Holliday stars in this
OL,7,     Fcomedy as a smalltown girl who
OL,8,     Fcomes to New York and rents a
OL,9,     Fbillboard to publicise her name -
OL,10,     Fand soon she's a TV star. With
OL,11,     FJack Lemmon.
